entries.femaleVariant: Did I see it? She damn near blew me off the road! Weather's gettin' crazier and crazier.
And it'll get worse. Know why?
Nature behaves just like any mother.
At first she's patient. Turns a blind eye to all kinds of shenanigans.
Then she'll tell you to cut it out, you'll ignore her again and again, 'til she's all riled up.
Keep that up an' she'll disown you. House you grew up in'll no longer be your home.
Look around. Who could feel at home here?
